title: Meta Platforms Asks Federal Court to Block FTC in Privacy Fight
description: The Facebook owner asked a federal court to block the Federal Trade Commission’s attempt to impose new sanctions on the company for alleged privacy violations.

title: Twitter Is Now Worth a Third of What Musk Paid For It, Fidelity Says
description: Social-media company’s value sinks to around $15 billion; Fidelity cuts its valuation for a third time.
